title: Sprout
desc:
- After 1 turn in your hand, turns into a <:brown:1107516362903007232> sprout.
- After 2 turns in your hand, turns into a <:green:1106234108042031166> + <:brown:1107516362903007232> sprout.
- After 3 turns in your hand, turns into a <:green:1106234108042031166> sprout.
- After 5 turns in your hand, turns into a <:brown:1107516362903007232> sprout.
- <:bones:1118750770133737565> and <:sprout:1118917438893985802> can be played on each other.
